                     <interp inst="t18150621-66-person594" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker Wilson pledged this handkerchief with me on the 22nd of May.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150621-66-person595">
                  THOMAS 
                  SMITH
